cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a system that involves ground robots and a micro aerial vehicle (MAV) for Search and Rescue (SaR) scenarios. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the system uses local visual servoing and different visual detection regimes. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the system involves autonomous operation and seamless transfer between ground robots. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper discusses the operability and return-home functionality of the system. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is also a possible category as the system involves multiple ground robots and a MAV working together.
